cpu: Intel(R) Core(TM) i7-9750H CPU @ 2.60GHz
BenchmarkDeleteSliceElms-12              1226868               978.2 ns/op           296 B/op         16 allocs/op
BenchmarkDeleteU64liceElms-12            8249469               145.3 ns/op            80 B/op          1 allocs/op
PASS
