原切片长度为 100：
BenchmarkDeleteSlice1-8          1652146               762.1 ns/op
BenchmarkDeleteSlice2-8          2124237               578.4 ns/op
BenchmarkDeleteSlice3-8          3161318               359.9 ns/op
